*[[USS South Dakota (BB-57)#Post-war|USS ''South Dakota'' (BB-57)]]<ref>'''USS ''South Dakota'' ''' is memorialized at Sioux Falls, S. Dak., where memorabilia and parts of the ship are displayed within an outline of the main deck. A screw from ''South Dakota'' is on display outside the [[U.S. Navy Museum#Willard Park|U.S. Navy Museum]] in Washington, D.C.</ref>
*[[USS Missouri (BB-63)#Museum ship (1993 to present)|Battleship ''Missouri'' Memorial]] <U+2013> USS Missouri (BB-63)
*[[Battleship New Jersey Museum and Memorial|Battleship ''New Jersey'' Museum and Memorial]] <U+2013> USS ''New Jersey'' (BB-62)
